《'''超脫'''》<ref>{{zh-tw}}{{cite web|url=https://www.sonymusic.com.tw/main/album/2014%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%B0%88%E8%BC%AF-%E8%B6%85%E8%84%AB-cddvd%E8%B1%AA%E8%8F%AF%E6%A5%B5%E8%87%B4%E7%89%88-%E9%BA%A5%E5%8F%AF%E5%82%91%E5%85%8B%E6%A3%AE-michael-jackson-88843066762|title=2014最新專輯 超脫 CD+DVD豪華極致版|work=sonymusic.com.tw|publisher=台灣索尼音樂娛樂股份有限公司|accessdate=2014-05-20}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>（{{lang-en|'''Xscape'''}}）是美國唱片藝術家[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]的第二張遺作[[合輯|合輯]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/3/31/5566496/new-michael-jackson-album-xscape-will-be-released-may-13th|work=The Verge|accessdate=2014-05-02|date=2014-03-31|title=New Michael Jackson album 'XSCAPE' will be released May 13th|first=Kwame|last=Opam|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509111644/https://www.theverge.com/2014/3/31/5566496/new-michael-jackson-album-xscape-will-be-released-may-13th|dead-url=no}}</ref>由[[Epic唱片|Epic唱片]]和{{link-en|MJJ Music|MJJ Music}}於2014年5月9日發行。這是[[索尼音樂娛樂|索尼]]和[[摩城唱片|摩城]]自[[麥可·傑克森之死|傑克森逝世]]於2009年6月後發行的第11張專輯。由Epic唱片總裁暨執行長{{link-en|L·A·里德|L.A. Reid}}擔任[[策劃人|策劃]]和[[執行製作人|執行製作人]]，邀請[[提姆巴蘭|提姆巴蘭]]帶領[[音樂製作人|製作團隊]]，包括{{link-en|Stargate (製作團隊)|Stargate (production team)|Stargate}}、{{link-en|J-Roc|J-Roc (record producer)|傑羅姆·“J-Roc”·哈蒙}}、約翰·麥克萊恩（John McClain）和{{link-en|羅德尼·傑金斯|Rodney Jerkins}}，來重新設計與集思八首已選定的歌曲。傑金斯製作主打歌，且這也是唯一完成最後的製作工作的原曲製作人。

《超脫》透過整個[[索尼|索尼集團]]的旗下公司來推廣；[[索尼行動通訊|索尼行動通訊]]使用〈愛的奴隸〉歌曲片段作為其[[Sony_Xperia_Z2|Sony Xperia Z2]]行動電話的宣傳廣告。首支主打單曲〈{{link-en|愛情從未如此美好|Love Never Felt So Good}}〉於2014年5月1日首度問世。豪華極致版包含所有歌曲的原始版本，外加一首附贈歌曲和兩支影片。

==背景==
2014年3月31日，正式宣布《超脫》包含8首歌曲。<ref name=officialannouncement>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.michaeljackson.com/us/news/xscape-new-album-coming-may-13th|title=XSCAPE: NEW ALBUM COMING MAY 13TH|date=2014-03-31|accessdate=2014-03-31|publisher=michaeljackson.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331175331/http://www.michaeljackson.com/us/news/xscape-new-album-coming-may-13th|archive-date=2014-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-26824983|title=New Michael Jackson album to be released in May|publisher=BBC News|year=2014|access-date=2014-05-20|archive-date=2021-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508221702/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-26824983|dead-url=no}}</ref>這是Epic Records在傑克森於2009年逝世後發行的第二張遺作專輯。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Chi |first=Chi |url=http://www.bbc.com/newsbeat/26831137 |title=Newsbeat – Michael Jackson new album Xscape: first listen |publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2014-04-03 |archive-date=2014-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404073950/http://www.bbc.com/newsbeat/26831137 |dead-url=no }}</ref>主打歌〈Xscape〉最初是為傑克森2001年的《[[Invincible_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Invincible]]》所錄製。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Farrar |first=Leah |url=http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/news/celebrity/2014/04/01/michael-jacksons-new-album-xscape-is-out-in-may |title=Michael Jackson new album Xscape release rumours |publisher=Glamour magazine |date=2011-10-18 |accessdate=2014-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140405092258/http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/news/celebrity/2014/04/01/michael-jacksons-new-album-xscape-is-out-in-may |archive-date=2014-04-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>由美國製作人[[提姆巴蘭|提姆巴蘭]]和[[Epic_Records|Epic Records]]的總裁{{link-en|L·A·里德|L.A. Reid}}負責監製，以及{{link-en|羅德尼·傑金斯|Rodney Jerkins}}、{{link-en|Stargate (製作團隊)|Stargate (production team)|Stargate}}和約翰·麥克萊恩（John McClain）。<ref name=timenews>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://time.com/43596/michael-jackson-xscape-new-music/|title=It's a Thriller: New Michael Jackson Songs Coming in May on Posthumous LP Xscape|author=Melissa Locker|date=2014-03-31|accessdate=2014-03-31|publisher=[[time.com|time.com]]|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084037/http://time.com/43596/michael-jackson-xscape-new-music/|dead-url=no}}</ref>提姆巴蘭表示里德曾親自到他家拜訪，討論新的傑克森的計畫。<ref name="Guardian Timbo Interview">{{en}}{{cite news |author=Guardian music |url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/aug/28/michael-jackson-timbaland-new-songs |title=New Michael Jackson music to be produced by Timbaland |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]] |date= |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008170249/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/aug/28/michael-jackson-timbaland-new-songs |dead-url=no }}</ref>美國樂團{{link-en|The Time (樂團)|The Time (band)|The Time}}的前主吉他手{{link-en|傑西·強生 (音樂家)|Jesse Johnson (musician)|傑西·強生}}透漏他正在和[[瑪麗·布萊姬|瑪麗·布萊姬]]、{{link-en|Questlove|Questlove}}以及{{link-en|D'Angelo|D'Angelo}}製作一首歌的元素。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7512603/michael-jackson-xscape-lp-child-abuse-high-profile-collabs#more-7512603|work=Idolator|publisher=Spin Media|date=2014-04-02|accessdate=2014-04-03|title=Michael Jackson's 'Xscape' LP Will Contain A Song About Child Abuse & High-Profile Collabs|last=Wass|first=Mike}}</ref>然而，這首歌並沒有包含在最終的專輯曲目清單中。里德表示他們想在命名這張專輯時讓傑克森的遺作增光，「這張專輯的名稱（《超脫》）遵循了麥可的專輯命名過程。從《[[Thriller_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Thriller]]》後，他總是挑選專輯中的一首歌來做為專輯名稱，且只用單一字詞，每一張（《[[Thriller_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Thriller]]》、《[[Bad_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Bad]]》、《[[Dangerous_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Dangerous]]》、《[[HIStory:_Past,_Present_and_Future,_Book_I|HIStory]]》、《[[Invincible_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Invincible]]》和《[[Michael_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Michael]]》）都有著前衛品質。而這張新專輯也是如此。」<ref name="Press Release">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/xscape-long-awaited-new-music-from-michael-jackson-253182181.html |title=XSCAPE-Long Awaited New Music From Michael Jackson – NEW YORK, 2014-03-31 /PRNewswire/ |publisher=Prnewswire.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2021-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509110436/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/xscape-long-awaited-new-music-from-michael-jackson-253182181.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==錄製歷史==
〈愛情從未如此美好〉由加拿大創作歌手[[保羅·安卡|保羅·安卡]]<ref name="Corner">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a567867/michael-jacksons-new-single-love-never-felt-so-good-gets-premiere-date.html |title=Michael Jackson's New Single 'Love Never Felt So Good' Gets Premiere Date |work=Digital Spy |publisher=Hearst Magazines |last=Corner |first=Lewis |date=2014-04-30 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924161246/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a567867/michael-jacksons-new-single-love-never-felt-so-good-gets-premiere-date.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和最初於1983年安卡鋼琴伴奏錄製的樣本共同寫成。這首歌同時也由美國藝人{{link-en|強尼·馬西斯|Johnny Mathis}}錄製而成。<ref name="Showbiz411.com">{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.showbiz411.com/2014/05/01/michael-jackson-new-single-written-with-paul-anka-is-actually-31-years-old |title=Michael Jackson 'New' Single Written with Paul Anka Is Actually 31 Years Old |work=Showbiz411.com |date=2014-05-01 |accessdate=2014-05-01 |archive-date=2014-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505011559/http://www.showbiz411.com/2014/05/01/michael-jackson-new-single-written-with-paul-anka-is-actually-31-years-old |dead-url=no }}</ref>〈芝加哥〉（原為〈She Was Loving Me〉）於1999年錄製，但卻未收錄於《[[Invincible_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Invincible]]》。〈愛著你〉於1987年《[[Bad_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|Bad]]》期間錄製。〈{{link-en|一個沒有名字的地方|A Place with No Name}}〉於1998年錄製與寫成。這首歌酷似美國搖滾樂團{{link-en|America (樂團)|America (band)|America}}的熱門歌曲〈{{link-en|A Horse with No Name|A Horse with No Name}}〉。這首歌的24秒片段於2009年7月在[[TMZ|TMZ]]網站上流出，且完整版本在2013年12月也被洩漏。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Business/MichaelJackson/Story?id=8107736&page=1|title=Michael Jackson's Unreleased Songs, Continuing the Music Legacy|work=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]/[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]]|publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] Internet Ventures, [[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]]—[[American_Broadcasting_Company|ABC]] News Network|date=2009-07-17|last=Netter|first=Sarah|accessdate=2014-01-07|archive-date=2009-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090817202058/http://abcnews.go.com/Business/MichaelJackson/story?id=8107736&page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈愛的奴隸〉也是在《Bad》其間錄製而成，然後在《Dangerous》時又重新錄製，並在1998年完成。這首歌在2010年流露到網路上。之後[[賈斯汀·比伯|賈斯汀·比伯]]<!-- 確實是賈斯汀·汀布萊克，請見參考來源。 -->與傑克森錄製的一首二重唱版本在2013年8月被洩漏。而麥可·傑克森遺產管理委員會並沒有授權發行這首歌，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Justin Bieber, Michael Jackson Duet: Estate Releases Statement|url=http://www.inquisitr.com/912400/justin-bieber-michael-jackson-slave-to-the-rhythm-estate-releases-statement/|work=The Inquisitr|accessdate=2013-08-22|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307080331/http://www.inquisitr.com/912400/justin-bieber-michael-jackson-slave-to-the-rhythm-estate-releases-statement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>並且試圖將這首歌從多數的網站和[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道上移除。

==促銷和單曲==
索尼和傑克森的遺產管理委員會在2014年2月宣布與[[索尼行動通訊|索尼行動通訊]]的合作關係，將會在推出的廣告中納入專輯中已確認的歌曲〈愛的奴隸〉的全新版本。<ref name=bbnews1>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6029371/new-michael-jackson-album-xscape-to-be-released-in-may|title=New Michael Jackson Album 'Xscape' to Be Released in May|date=2014-03-31|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2014-03-31|archive-date=2014-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140401162659/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6029371/new-michael-jackson-album-xscape-to-be-released-in-may|dead-url=no}}</ref>這是廣告是為[[索尼行動通訊|索尼行動通訊]]的[[Sony_Xperia_Z2|Xperia Z2]]行動電話所推出的。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.michaeljackson.com/us/news/estate-michael-jackson-enters-partnership-sony-mobile|title=THE ESTATE OF MICHAEL JACKSON ENTERS PARTNERSHIP WITH SONY MOBILE|publisher=michaeljackson.com|work=[[Sony_Entertainment|Sony Entertainment]]|access-date=2014-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407060051/http://www.michaeljackson.com/us/news/estate-michael-jackson-enters-partnership-sony-mobile|archive-date=2014-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>這張專輯也已經於2014年3月31日在一間[[騎士橋|騎士橋]]的飯店地下室中播放給英國媒體聆聽。記者將能在不攜帶任何電子裝置的情況下聆聽這張專輯一次，且所有歌曲的名稱是不對外透漏的。<ref name=standardeve>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/goingout/music/michael-jacksons-new-album-xscape-gets-its-first-hearing-9227726.html|title=Michael Jackson's 'new' album Xscape gets its first hearing|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-04-01|first=David |last=Smyth|newspaper=[[London_Evening_Standard|London Evening Standard]]}}</ref>一些英國的娛樂記者，像是《[[天空新聞台|天空新聞台]]》、<ref name=skynews>{{en}}{{cite web|url=https://uk.news.yahoo.com/michael-jackson-xscape-album-due-may-145547119.html#xZxRpVq|title=Michael Jackson Xscape Album Due Out In May|publisher=[[Yahoo!_UK_&_Ireland|Yahoo! UK & Ireland]]|work=[[Sky_News|Sky News]]|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-04-01|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925223645/https://uk.news.yahoo.com/michael-jackson-xscape-album-due-may-145547119.html#xZxRpVq|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[倫敦旗幟晚報|倫敦旗幟晚報]]》、<ref name=standardeve />《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》、<ref name=tele>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/michael-jackson/10735331/Michael-Jackson-new-album-Xscape-first-listen.html|title=Michael Jackson new album Xscape: first listen|date=2014-03-31|accessdate=2014-04-01|first=Bernadette|last=McNulty|newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=[[Telegraph_Media_Group|Telegraph Media Group]]|location=London, England|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509110521/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/michael-jackson/10735331/Michael-Jackson-new-album-Xscape-first-listen.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《{{link-en|Mixmag|Mixmag}}》、<ref name=Mixmag />《[[衛報|衛報]]》<ref name=guardian>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2014/apr/01/first-listen-michael-jackson-xscape|title=First listen: Michael Jackson's Xscape|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-04-05|first=Michael|last=Cragg|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|location=London, England|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509110524/https://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2014/apr/01/first-listen-michael-jackson-xscape|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]<ref name=DigitalSpy>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/music/feature/a561541/michael-jacksons-new-album-xscape-how-good-is-it.html|title=Michael Jackson's new album Xscape: How good is it?|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-04-01|first=Lewis|last=Corner|work=Digital Spy|publisher=[[Hearst_Corporation|Hearst Magazines UK]]|archive-date=2015-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025154503/http://www.digitalspy.com.au/music/feature/a561541/michael-jacksons-new-album-xscape-how-good-is-it.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>皆在受邀名單內。

