ny_(magazine)|Ebony]] |date=2014-04-01 |accessdate=2014-04-05 |first=Michael |last=Arceneaux |publisher=[[Johnson_Publishing_Company|Johnson Publishing Company]] |location=Chicago, USA |journal= |archive-date=2018-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009211200/https://www.ebony.com/entertainment-culture/the-weekly-read-leave-michael-jackson-alone-032 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的埃麗莎·加德納（Elysa Gardner）表示這張專輯的製作人「擔保將描繪出傑克森歷久不衰的歌手實力，現代電子製作元素並沒有蓋過那獨特、使人顫慄的嗓音，也沒有破壞歌曲的總體結構。」<ref name="USA Today">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/04/21/first-listen-michael-jackson-posthumous-xscape/7553229/|work=USA Today|publisher=Gannett Company|accessdate=2014-04-26|date=2014-04-21|title=First listen: Michael Jackson's posthumous 'Xscape'|first=Elysa|last=Gardner|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509110301/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/04/21/first-listen-michael-jackson-posthumous-xscape/7553229/|dead-url=no}}</ref>其他評論家認為這張專輯只是推銷索尼智慧型手機的一種方式，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/05/13/michael-jackson-s-posthumous-album-xscape-is-a-confused-shameless-money-grab.html|title=Michael Jackson’s Posthumous Album, ‘Xscape,’ Is a Confused, Shameless Money Grab|first=Andrew|last=Romano|date=2014-05-13|work=thedailybeast.com|publisher=he Daily Beast Company LLC|accessdate=2014-05-20|archive-date=2017-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404233950/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/05/13/michael-jackson-s-posthumous-album-xscape-is-a-confused-shameless-money-grab.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>並在寫歌與製作上，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/michael-jacksons-xscape-album-why-it-adds-nothing-to-a-legends-legacy|title=Michael Jackson's 'Xscape' Album: Why It Adds Nothing To A Legend's Legacy|first=Ben|last=Hewitt|work=nme.com|publisher=IPC Media Entertainment Network|date=2014-05-09|accessdate=2014-05-20|archive-date=2016-08-21